        "content": "<p><code>OfNat</code> for <code>Fin</code> is defined like this:</p>\n<div class=\"codehilite\" data-code-language=\"Lean4\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"kn\">instance</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">instOfNat</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">OfNat</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"n\">Fin</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"n\">no_index</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"n\">n</span><span class=\"bp\">+</span><span class=\"mi\">1</span><span class=\"o\">)))</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">i</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"kn\">where</span>\n<span class=\"w\">  </span><span class=\"n\">ofNat</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">:=</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">Fin</span><span class=\"bp\">.</span><span class=\"n\">ofNat</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">i</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<p>What does the <code>no_index</code> keyword mean/do?</p>",
        "id": 473202777,
        "sender_full_name": "Tom",
        "timestamp": 1727468459
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>It controls how the \"discrimination tree key\" is generated for this instance.</p>\n<p>The accelerator data structure for instance lookup is called a discrimination tree, and it is used for only needing to consider instances that <em>structurally</em> have the correct form. <code>no_index</code> makes that particular spot in the structure be a wildcard. So, it'll apply whenever <code>OfNat (Fin *) *</code> matches rather than the stricter <code>OfNat (Fin (* + 1)) *</code>.</p>",
        "id": 473204047,
        "sender_full_name": "Kyle Miller",
        "timestamp": 1727468737
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>Well, in theory. It looks like <code>n + 1</code> might not need such a <code>no_index</code>?</p>\n<div class=\"codehilite\" data-code-language=\"Lean4\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"bp\">#</span><span class=\"n\">discr_tree_key</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"n\">n</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">i</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">Nat</span><span class=\"o\">)</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">→</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">OfNat</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"n\">Fin</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"n\">no_index</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"n\">n</span><span class=\"bp\">+</span><span class=\"mi\">1</span><span class=\"o\">)))</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">i</span>\n<span class=\"c1\">-- OfNat (Fin _) _</span>\n\n<span class=\"bp\">#</span><span class=\"n\">discr_tree_key</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"n\">n</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">i</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">Nat</span><span class=\"o\">)</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">→</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">OfNat</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"n\">Fin</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"n\">n</span><span class=\"bp\">+</span><span class=\"mi\">1</span><span class=\"o\">))</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">i</span>\n<span class=\"c1\">-- OfNat (Fin _) _</span>\n</code></pre></div>",
        "id": 473204696,
        "sender_full_name": "Kyle Miller",
        "timestamp": 1727468875
    },
